&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot; data-start=&quot;1681&quot; data-end=&quot;1716&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You’ll spend your days outside, working on diverse natural landscapes and seeing real environmental improvements take shape under your hands.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
