&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Maintenance and mowing of solar fields through equipment operation and herbicide application.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
