&lt;p data-start=&quot;954&quot; data-end=&quot;1267&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This is a hands-on role where you’ll spend most of your time (about 70%) engaging directly with field crews, ensuring their safety and compliance, and coaching them toward best practices. You’ll also provide office-based support (about 30%) by managing safety records, training programs, and compliance systems.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1269&quot; data-end=&quot;1562&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You’ll be a trusted resource to both field teams and leadership, balancing proactive prevention with responsive solutions when incidents occur. If you’re energized by travel, working outdoors, and helping crews stay safe while delivering high-impact ecological projects, this job is for you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
