&lt;li&gt;Help shape the future of the Midwest Region through leadership continuity and operational growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with experienced project managers, operators, and regional leadership teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Play a critical role in maintaining client relationships and delivery excellence across a rapidly expanding portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
